    "description": "Zoo Seeker是融合了过去、现在、未来的奇幻风格背景和兽人形态角色的世界。<br><br>神用画笔创造了世界，在为创造的世界注入生命的过程中猫咪们闯祸了。<br><br>由于猫咪们闯的祸，神使用的颜料被带到了世界各地，看着垂头丧气的神，猫咪们为了寻找隐藏在各个世界里的颜料而去旅行。<br><br>■ 探索各种各样的世界吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/f05563abd6dac77778adb21c1c3c076a.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/f05563abd6dac77778adb21c1c3c076a.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/f05563abd6dac77778adb21c1c3c076a.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>可以探索許多世界。<br><br><br>■ 寻找隐藏在各个世界里的史莱姆吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/87dcebf2c27bd9d7e2adf146091914ca.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/87dcebf2c27bd9d7e2adf146091914ca.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/87dcebf2c27bd9d7e2adf146091914ca.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>史莱姆藏起来了。睁大眼睛找一找吧。<br><br><br>■ 找到所有的史莱姆把颜料还给神！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7900d8cca3f00bb1ad86e02e2a414e5c.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7900d8cca3f00bb1ad86e02e2a414e5c.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7900d8cca3f00bb1ad86e02e2a414e5c.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果把隐藏的史莱姆都找出来，他们就会变成颜料。神会很高兴的。<br><br> <br>■ 利用各种提示找到最后吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/b01dfd7d01ca840bcd4990afe4e8feb2.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/b01dfd7d01ca840bcd4990afe4e8feb2.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/b01dfd7d01ca840bcd4990afe4e8feb2.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>关卡模式不限制提示数 。<br>挑战模式只能利用5个提示。<br><br><br>■ 开始挑战模式创造记录吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7e63aa2d3e2427b6add3b16d1f3fbc4d.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7e63aa2d3e2427b6add3b16d1f3fbc4d.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/7e63aa2d3e2427b6add3b16d1f3fbc4d.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>挑战模式与关卡模式中不同的道具位置会发生改变。<br>挑战模式会记录游戏时间。<br><br>■ 利用地图编辑创造世界吧!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/247c8cc63915873ec31bb7ca4bac5257.poster.avif?t=1643251095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/247c8cc63915873ec31bb7ca4bac5257.webm?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789180/extras/247c8cc63915873ec31bb7ca4bac5257.mp4?t=1643251095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>完成的主题越多，就可以使用更多的功能。",
